flowchart TD
    A[EventSource] --> B[Global Middleware]
    B --> C[EventRouter&lt;Event&gt;]

    C -->|ChatMessage| D[ChatProjector: Event -&gt; ChatRequest]
    D --> E[Chat Middleware]
    E --> F[ChatRouter&lt;ChatRequest&gt;]
    F -->|Plain| G[PlainMessageHandler]
    F -->|Command| H[CommandProjector: ChatRequest -&gt; CommandRequest]
    H --> I[Command Middleware]
    I --> J[CommandRouter]
    J -->|music| K[MusicHandler]
    J -->|skip| L[SkipHandler]
    J -->|fallback| M[UnknownCommandHandler]

    C -->|RewardRedemption| N[RewardProjector: Event -&gt; RewardRequest]
    N --> O[Reward Middleware]
    O --> P[RewardRouter&lt;RewardRequest&gt;]
    P -->|reward_1| Q[Reward1Handler]
    P -->|reward_2| R[Reward2Handler]
    P -->|reward_n| S[RewardNHandler]

    C -->|System / Unsupported| T[SystemProjector: Event -&gt; SystemRequest]
    T --> U[SystemHandler]

    C -->|Subscribe| V[SubscriptionProjector]
    V --> W[Subscription Middleware]
    W --> X[SubscriptionHandler]

    C -->|Raid| Y[RaidProjector]
    Y --> Z[Raid Middleware]
    Z --> AA[RaidHandler]
